Type: Package
Package: happifn
Title: Interface to French 'IFN' data
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Paul", "Carteron", , "carteronpaul@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6942-6662"))
Maintainer: Paul Carteron <carteronpaul@gmail.com>
Description: Allows you to import raw data from the permanent plots of the
    french National Forest Inventory (IFN)
    <https://inventaire-forestier.ign.fr/dataifn> and the spatial contours
    of the major forest groupings.
